Yocto environment for building raspberry pi images. 

1) Install required dependencies for yocto to run bitbake https://www.yoctoproject.org/docs/1.8/yocto-project-qs/yocto-project-qs.html

2) Check out the code and initialize submodules

3) Run the init script to set u your workspace

4) create your first image with bitbake rpi-basic-image 
